{"tid":196921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓警告若美有任何軍事行動     或以核武反擊","createTime":"2017-04-11T15:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T16:57:22.000Z","uid":58099,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb3d0ee45beb477cea64617948e27dbf888d208","tid":196921,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"北韓警告若美有任何侵略行動 或以核武反擊<br />\n　2017-04-11 22:50<br />\n<br />\n北韓警告，若有任何跡象顯示，美國將採取先發制人攻擊，北韓可能會以核武攻擊美國。<br />\n<br />\n北韓官方電視台，首次回應美國派航空母艦「卡爾文森號」戰鬥群駛往朝鮮半島附近，指證明美國準備入侵北韓的魯莽行動，已達到嚴重階段。<br />\n<br />\n勞動新聞報道，當局準備回應美國的任何侵略行動，又指核彈瞄準美國在南韓及太平洋作戰中心的侵略基地，還有美國本土的基地。"},{"pid":"6220f82721baba07b1e79f9768d7e4749fb81926","tid":196921,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5b31484d914ce68dd9c131b4f82272c3e018cc7","tid":196921,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"金仔瀨緊屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d99f04f27677bcd2ddb616e3346d6f7d57cfbf","tid":196921,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa2370883810566596653392be7d25087c222f4a","tid":196921,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"你射去北京都射唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去美國&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd63a176b70ee2f294d0a56ab9187f8258252fb7","tid":196921,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"Let's shout午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceafadf76a9c8cf213b0f7844b17af56ea21ce0e","tid":196921,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"講真, 到北韓D核彈可以射到去美國果時先黎打, 已經太撚遲<br />\n跟本而家打已經係最好既時機<br />\n而家唔打, 下屆換